		"description": "<p>Having spent too much time around necromantic magic or the undead themselves, and it has now affected you in a more permanent way, and as such:</p><ul><li><p>You gain the undead creature type.</p></li><li><p>You gain resistance to necrotic damage.</p></li><li><p>You gain immunity to both poison damage and the poisoned condition.</p></li><li><p>You no longer require sleep, but instead, during a long rest you sit or stand motionless for at least 4 hours. You remain conscious during this time.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>You do not need to eat or drink.</p></li><li><p>You suffer no ill effects from resurrection magic, and resurrection magic used on you does not require material components.</p></li></ul>",
